io.spine.code.gen

Class IndentLevel

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.spine.code.gen.IndentLevel

  • public final class IndentLevel
extends java.lang.Object
    An indent level, which determines a number of indents to align code with.

    The value cannot be negative.
